com.chrismin13.additionsapi.durability

Class FishingRodDurability

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chrismin13.additionsapi.durability.ItemDurability
      • com.chrismin13.additionsapi.durability.FishingRodDurability

  • public class FishingRodDurability
extends ItemDurability
    This specifies how a Fishing Rod will have its durability reduced when performing certain actions. Default values are set up exactly like in vanilla Minecraft.
    BlockBreak defaults to 0
    EntityHit defautls to 0
    Fish Catch defaults to 1
    Block Reel defaults to 2
    Item Reel defaults to 3
    Entity Reel defaults to 5
    Author:
    chrismin13
